<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.9">
<l>vaḻakkeṉa niṉaimiṉ valviṉai mūḻkā</l>
<l>taḻakkoṭi yaṭṭā ṉamarperuṅ kōyiṉ</l>
<l>maḻakkaḷiṟ ṟiṉañcēr māliruñ cōlai</l>
<l>toḻukkaru tuvatē tuṇivatu cūtē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Think [this is] the custom with sinking into cruel deeds/karma.</l>
<l>The means(?) is being determined to be intent on worship</l>
<l>in Māliruñcōlai joined by herds of young elephant bulls,</l>
<l>the great temple where abides he who killed the demoness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
